    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Book of Abominations</strong> is a monster taming JRPG steeped in Eldritch horror. After arriving on the remote Halflight Isle to inherit a house left by a distant relative, the player unwittingly unleashes the monster apocalypse from the pages of a dusty old tome. It is up to you to capture these abominations, explore this mysterious island and discover the secrets of the book!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/6cf6b323576388a4fb820fb97dbed3dc.poster.avif?t=1762941977\" width=464 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/6cf6b323576388a4fb820fb97dbed3dc.webm?t=1762941977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/6cf6b323576388a4fb820fb97dbed3dc.mp4?t=1762941977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/bd9cd81c03dbd042cfb045b5da9a96ef.avif?t=1762941977\" width=510 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master your control over the Book of Abominations: battle and capture a series of grotesque yet adorably charming Eldritch horrors in fast-paced, dynamic JRPG inspired turn based combat!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill your bestiary: capture Lovecraftian abominations and mutate them through combat encounters to take on more powerful forms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize each monster's array of attacks and abilities to implement various status effects, buffs and debuffs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat bosses in one-off fights to gain powerful summons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of charms to give your monster party unique advantages in battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/e0a5add363c113fb4c3265731f1f3466.poster.avif?t=1762941977\" width=464 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/e0a5add363c113fb4c3265731f1f3466.webm?t=1762941977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/e0a5add363c113fb4c3265731f1f3466.mp4?t=1762941977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/338ae64f645b05943e1b43c7723dd305.avif?t=1762941977\" width=510 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Haflight Isle - a once prosperous fishing community shrouded in a history of supernatural, otherworldly horror.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet and befriend a colourful cast of NPCs, both humans and monsters alike!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find benevolent monsters and use the powers they bestow to solve puzzles and reach new areas of the island.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover secrets in far-flung corners of the map, finding a variety of collectibles to assist in combat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/dfdbdb94eba99a87ad611d2fb3849c79.poster.avif?t=1762941977\" width=464 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/dfdbdb94eba99a87ad611d2fb3849c79.webm?t=1762941977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291120/extras/dfdbdb94eba99a87ad611d2fb3849c79.mp4?t=1762941977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
